Uses of Package
GUI.src

  • Classes in GUI.src used by GUI.src 
    Class and Description
    Klima
    The Klima class for the temperature display.
    Licht
    The Licht class contains all logical functionalities and graphical displays of lights in rooms.
    Modul
    The Modul class contains the current light and temperature data of the module in a room, it is updated with data received from the WSN.
    Raum
    The Raum class contains all the variables for a room (such as Licht, Modul and Klima), as well as a constructor.
